{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve confirmed there isn\u2019t any real composition execution loop yet: `composition_jobs` exist, but they\u2019re only seeded and marked in-progress, with no worker-owned progression, no pause/resume control path, and no partial draft persistenc...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_46", "text": "I\u2019ve confirmed there isn\u2019t any real composition execution loop yet: `composition_jobs` exist, but they\u2019re only seeded and marked in-progress, with no worker-owned progression, no pause/resume control path, and no partial draft persistence. Next I\u2019m reading storage and worker extension points so I can add an actual resumable execution service instead of inventing a second job model.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 92, "prompt_index": 61, "prompt_name": "60 \u2014 Composition Job Orchestration", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T05:58:10-07:00"}
