{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I have the orchestration shape now: a `CompositionJob` will become the durable source of truth, while short-lived `background_jobs` act as resumable execution attempts that advance the composition one segment at a time. I\u2019m moving into i...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_80", "text": "I have the orchestration shape now: a `CompositionJob` will become the durable source of truth, while short-lived `background_jobs` act as resumable execution attempts that advance the composition one segment at a time. I\u2019m moving into implementation: start/redirect will queue a composition job plus seeded segment rows, and pause/resume/cancel will mutate the durable composition record the worker reads on each attempt.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 159, "prompt_index": 61, "prompt_name": "60 \u2014 Composition Job Orchestration", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T06:06:46-07:00"}
