{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I found one subtle queueing risk while writing the tests: a pause/resume cycle can create duplicate runtime attempts if we blindly enqueue on every resume. I\u2019m fixing that now by deduplicating queued composition runtime jobs per `composi...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_128", "text": "I found one subtle queueing risk while writing the tests: a pause/resume cycle can create duplicate runtime attempts if we blindly enqueue on every resume. I\u2019m fixing that now by deduplicating queued composition runtime jobs per `composition_job_id` so the durable composition record stays the only execution source of truth.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 269, "prompt_index": 61, "prompt_name": "60 \u2014 Composition Job Orchestration", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T06:25:43-07:00"}
